name: ascend
audience: public
description: >
  AI-powered engineering management CLI. Team tracking, performance
  snapshots, 1:1 coaching, meeting transcript analysis, risk detection,
  and schedule management. TUI built with Textual.

domains:
  - engineering-management
  - team-analytics
  - coaching
  - tui
  - claude-ai-integration

voice:
  tone: supportive, data-driven, action-oriented
  principles:
    - Coaching grounded in observed patterns, not assumptions
    - Performance snapshots are descriptive, not evaluative
    - Risk detection flags early, never after the fact
    - Meeting transcripts yield actionable items, not summaries
  anti-patterns:
    - Surveillance framing — this is a coaching tool, not monitoring
    - Generating coaching without transcript/data backing
    - Storing raw transcripts beyond extraction

standards:
  code_review:
    - Pydantic models for all data structures
    - SQLite for local persistence
    - Claude API for summarization and coaching
  documentation:
    - CLI commands documented with examples

connects_to:
  - kindex
